		<body>
			<pb n='1'/>
			<p>
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_1_1l1' n='N001'/>Songs from a Free Space“
			</p>
			<p>
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_2_1l1' n='N001'/>Astrology Hype
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_2_1l2' n='N002'/>Corole Ramer
			</p>
			<p>
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_3_1l1' n='N001'/>While in prison six months
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_3_1l2' n='N002'/>my horoscope predicted:
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_3_1l3' n='N003'/>&quot;Travel to exciting places.
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_3_1l4' n='N004'/>New career opportunities.
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_3_1l5' n='N005'/>Romance and adventure.&quot;
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_3_1l6' n='N006'/>So far—l&apos;ve traveled from jail
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_3_1l7' n='N007'/>to Manhattan Supreme Court.
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_3_1l8' n='N008'/>My pay scale has increased from 10 to 259 per hour.
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_3_1l9' n='N009'/>Numerous other inmates have made
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_3_1l10' n='N010'/>overtly sexual advances to me
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_3_1l11' n='N011'/>in vacant stairwells.
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_3_1l12' n='N012'/>Honey,
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_3_1l13' n='N013'/>that&apos;s not my idea of a rising sign.
			</p>
			<p>
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_8_1l1' n='N001'/>*From Songs From a Free Space/Writings by Women in
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_8_1l2' n='N002'/>Prison, edited by Carol Muske and Gail Rosenblum, New
				<lb facs='#facs_1_r_8_1l3' n='N003'/>Vork, n.d.
			</p>
